    <dlgPart>
      <portrait />
      <speaker_name />
      <npc_text>“Have you come to pray, &lt;brother/sister&gt;?” asks the man, chanting the words. “Have you come to marvel at That Which Has Been Spared Their Wrath? Have you come to Ask Why?”</npc_text>
